<package name="ds4drv" project="openSUSE:Factory">
  <title>ds4drv is a Sony DualShock 4 userspace driver for Linux.</title>
  <description>Option to emulate the Xbox 360 controller for compatibility with Steam games
Setting the LED color
Reminding you about low battery by flashing the LED
Using the trackpad as a mouse
Custom mappings, map buttons and sticks to whatever mouse, key or joystick action you want
Settings profiles that can be cycled through with a button binding </description>
  <url>https://github.com/chrippa/ds4drv</url>
</package>
